# Frontend Interview Preparation Repository

This repository contains the interview questions I have encountered during real interview processes for Frontend/Senior Frontend Engineer roles.

## What's Included

* Interview questions asked by different companies.
* Company-wise interview experiences.
* JavaScript interview questions.
* React.js interview questions.
* TypeScript interview questions.
* HTML & CSS interview questions.
* System Design and Frontend Architecture questions.
* Coding and machine coding problems.
* Behavioral and HR interview questions.

## Purpose

The goal of this repository is to:

* Keep a record of the interviews I have attended.
* Document the actual questions asked during interviews.
* Track my preparation and learning.
* Help with future interview preparation and revisions.

> **Note:** The content in this repository is based on my personal interview experiences and preparation. The questions are shared for learning and revision purposes only.
